6
00:00:25,250 --> 00:00:26,280
You don't have to worry about me.

7
00:00:26,280 --> 00:00:27,480
How can I not worry?

8
00:00:33,520 --> 00:00:34,520
Your mother said

9
00:00:35,880 --> 00:00:37,480
that whenever you're troubled,

10
00:00:37,480 --> 00:00:38,880
you will come here alone.

11
00:00:41,670 --> 00:00:42,240
Tell me,

12
00:00:43,210 --> 00:00:43,870
what

13
00:00:44,920 --> 00:00:45,520
happened?

14
00:00:49,790 --> 00:00:50,390
Nothing.

15
00:00:51,000 --> 00:00:51,790
I just

16
00:00:52,920 --> 00:00:54,470
wanted to talk to my dad.

17
00:00:59,990 --> 00:01:00,410
Okay.

18
00:01:01,390 --> 00:01:02,790
Then I'll accompany you.

19
00:01:03,350 --> 00:01:04,069
Actually,

20
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:06,690
I have something to say to him, too.

21
00:01:07,930 --> 00:01:09,330
What are you going to say?

22
00:01:11,810 --> 00:01:12,930
I'll tell him that Corn

23
00:01:12,930 --> 00:01:14,050
has grown up.

24
00:01:14,590 --> 00:01:15,950
She can earn money on her own

25
00:01:15,950 --> 00:01:17,590
and take care of herself.

26
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:21,320
He doesn't need to worry about her anymore.

27
00:01:23,510 --> 00:01:24,230
But

28
00:01:25,160 --> 00:01:26,490
I can't run fast enough.

29
00:01:31,590 --> 00:01:33,850
Are you sad because of those two minutes?

30
00:01:40,870 --> 00:01:41,350
Dad,

31
00:01:41,640 --> 00:01:42,500
what happened?

32
00:01:43,759 --> 00:01:44,280
Dad!

33
00:01:47,310 --> 00:01:47,789
Dad!

34
00:01:48,509 --> 00:01:49,070
Dad!

35
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:51,509
Is anyone there?

36
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:53,580
Is anybody here?

37
00:01:57,979 --> 00:01:59,840
Dad, I'll ask someone to save you.

38
00:02:03,400 --> 00:02:04,120
Hurry up.

39
00:02:04,250 --> 00:02:05,380
We're almost there.

40
00:02:07,870 --> 00:02:09,070
It's just over there.

41
00:02:10,000 --> 00:02:10,400
Dad!

42
00:02:10,580 --> 00:02:11,380
Hang in there.

43
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:11,910
Dad!

44
00:02:12,930 --> 00:02:14,080
Go a little deeper.

45
00:02:18,750 --> 00:02:20,470
Go a bit further.

46
00:02:21,310 --> 00:02:22,240
Please.

47
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:24,040
Please, keep searching for him.

48
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:27,630
I'm begging you

49
00:02:27,630 --> 00:02:29,300
to keep searching.

50
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:32,560
I beg you, please save my father.

51
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:36,000
Dad!

52
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:42,800
We got him out too late.

53
00:02:43,630 --> 00:02:45,360
If it were two minutes earlier,

54
00:02:45,550 --> 00:02:47,280
there might have been a chance.

55
00:02:57,360 --> 00:02:58,490
I keep thinking that

56
00:03:00,630 --> 00:03:02,710
if I had been two minutes faster,

57
00:03:04,740 --> 00:03:06,350
would my father still be alive?

58
00:03:06,350 --> 00:03:08,470
♪ Run down ♪

59
00:03:07,050 --> 00:03:08,370
It's not your fault.

60
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,550
