61
00:03:10,400 --> 00:03:11,800
Every time I come here,

62
00:03:12,750 --> 00:03:14,120
I always think of that day.

63
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:15,050
♪ When I set out ♪

64
00:03:15,630 --> 00:03:17,590
