65
00:03:16,100 --> 00:03:18,100
♪ You didn't know ♪

66
00:03:19,380 --> 00:03:24,310
♪ That I cared so deeply and I drew ♪

67
00:03:21,710 --> 00:03:23,590
I know I shouldn't think this way,

68
00:03:23,940 --> 00:03:25,570
but I can't help myself.

69
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:30,940
♪ So neatly when I pictured me with you ♪

70
00:03:34,570 --> 00:03:38,329
♪ My eyes falling like leaves ♪

71
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:41,930
♪ You delicate as thieves ♪

72
00:03:42,050 --> 00:03:45,570
♪ Who would have ever believed ♪

73
00:03:47,290 --> 00:03:50,320
♪ That love goes small ♪

74
00:03:50,360 --> 00:03:53,930
♪ After you knowing it tall ♪

75
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:53,240
But it's okay.

76
00:03:55,150 --> 00:03:58,930
♪ Eyes on the prize you win it all ♪

77
00:03:55,590 --> 00:03:57,120
The competition is coming.

78
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,930
Attending the competition

79
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:06,380
♪ We never were, we never will ♪

80
00:04:01,190 --> 00:04:02,850
is a way for me to find closure.

81
00:04:04,030 --> 00:04:05,690
It will also let my father know

82
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,530
