83
00:04:09,180 --> 00:04:14,460
♪ Be anywhere other than where we are still ♪

84
00:04:14,870 --> 00:04:20,220
♪ We won't progress or get serious ♪

85
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,089
Have breakfast?

86
00:04:22,200 --> 00:04:25,990
♪ Like all our friends will ♪

87
00:05:56,230 --> 00:05:59,140
[Close to You]

88
00:05:59,170 --> 00:06:01,580
[Episode 24 We will all have a good future]

89
00:06:03,870 --> 00:06:04,950
Auntie Jiang.

90
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,480
I miss you so much.

91
00:06:08,510 --> 00:06:09,760
I miss you, too.

92
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:10,780
Have a seat.

93
00:06:14,950 --> 00:06:16,830
It has been four years.

94
00:06:17,000 --> 00:06:18,160
Why did you suddenly come back?

95
00:06:18,160 --> 00:06:20,040
You didn't even tell us in advance.

96
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:20,840
Auntie Jiang,

97
00:06:20,870 --> 00:06:23,040
you're the one I missed the most while I was abroad.

98
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:25,720
But I've been quite busy since I returned.

99
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:28,530
I didn't have time to meet up with you until today.

100
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:31,010
I regret not having a daughter.

101
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:32,900
If I had one as considerate as you,

102
00:06:33,150 --> 00:06:34,310
I would be happy.

103
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:36,670
Jiang Bohan is very filial, too.

104
00:06:36,670 --> 00:06:37,280
He's just,

105
00:06:37,310 --> 00:06:38,510
you know, stubborn with his words.

106
00:06:38,510 --> 00:06:40,040
He cares about you a lot.

107
00:06:40,600 --> 00:06:41,480
He still

108
00:06:41,480 --> 00:06:42,880
opposes me at every turn.

109
00:06:43,159 --> 00:06:43,820
Otherwise,

110
00:06:43,990 --> 00:06:45,820
why would I ask for your help?

111
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,130
Well,

112
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:49,780
did you meet that girl?

113
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:51,390
Yes.

114
00:06:52,860 --> 00:06:54,860
I think she took my words seriously.

115
00:06:57,210 --> 00:06:59,380
Yu Mingxi is a good girl.

116
00:07:00,430 --> 00:07:01,070
She is hardworking,

117
00:07:01,070 --> 00:07:01,680
strong,

118
00:07:02,190 --> 00:07:03,120
and optimistic.

119
00:07:04,270 --> 00:07:05,000
Actually,

120
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,370
I like her very much.

121
00:07:07,750 --> 00:07:09,560
But as a mother,

122
00:07:10,160 --> 00:07:12,510
I have to be a bit selfish sometimes.

123
00:07:13,310 --> 00:07:14,000
I will

124
00:07:14,420 --> 00:07:16,500
definitely prioritize my son.

125
00:07:17,430 --> 00:07:20,230
Everyone understands parents' good intentions.

126
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,480
Besides, if she can go abroad,

127
00:07:22,690 --> 00:07:24,810
it would be a good thing for her.

128
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:27,160
So you don't have to think too much.

129
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:30,920
Hope it all goes as we wish.

130
00:07:31,390 --> 00:07:31,870
It will.

131
00:07:32,990 --> 00:07:33,920
The food here is delicious.

132
00:07:33,920 --> 00:07:34,400
Try it.

133
00:07:34,430 --> 00:07:34,830
Okay.

134
00:07:41,810 --> 00:07:43,270
I'll send you the address.

135
00:08:00,180 --> 00:08:01,040
Headmistress,

136
00:08:01,470 --> 00:08:02,040
Senior,

137
00:08:02,830 --> 00:08:03,960
I've made up my mind.

138
00:08:04,600 --> 00:08:05,860
I'm willing to join you

139
00:08:06,230 --> 00:08:08,310
to persuade Jiang Bohan to study abroad.

140
00:08:08,310 --> 00:08:08,950
Really?

141
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:11,480
I'm so happy you're willing to help.

142
00:08:12,350 --> 00:08:12,910
However,

143
00:08:13,510 --> 00:08:14,440
I have a request.

144
00:08:14,800 --> 00:08:16,200
I hope you can agree to it.

145
00:08:17,150 --> 00:08:18,270
If you're willing,

146
00:08:18,450 --> 00:08:19,740
I can help you with your university application

147
00:08:19,740 --> 00:08:21,830
so that you can go abroad with Jiang Bohan.

148
00:08:21,830 --> 00:08:22,280
Yes.

149
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:23,750
Don't worry about money.

150
00:08:23,750 --> 00:08:25,480
Feel free to make any requests.

151
00:08:26,230 --> 00:08:27,150
No.

152
00:08:27,540 --> 00:08:28,870
You've misunderstood.

153
00:08:31,000 --> 00:08:32,929
I won't go abroad with Jiang Bohan.

154
00:08:36,770 --> 00:08:37,740
I only want

155
00:08:38,630 --> 00:08:40,429
you to tell a lie together with me

156
00:08:41,850 --> 00:08:43,549
and keep this secret.

157
00:09:12,120 --> 00:09:13,440
What are you thinking about?

158
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,640
You don't look happy.

159
00:09:14,890 --> 00:09:17,480
Is it too boring to watch them play basketball?

160
00:09:17,480 --> 00:09:17,880
No.

161
00:09:17,910 --> 00:09:19,770
I'm thinking about the marathon.

162
00:09:24,440 --> 00:09:26,170
Let me treat you to a meal later.

163
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:28,750
Have you finished your training today?

164
00:09:28,750 --> 00:09:30,500
Training doesn't interfere with important matters.

165
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:32,230
Having food is more important.

166
00:09:35,000 --> 00:09:36,460
Let me take you somewhere.

167
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:37,370
Let's go.

168
00:09:42,340 --> 00:09:42,870
Captain,

169
00:09:43,360 --> 00:09:44,470
where are you going?

170
00:09:44,470 --> 00:09:45,080
On a date.

171
00:09:48,120 --> 00:09:49,650
Is your knee still hurting?

172
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:51,050
Much better.

173
00:09:51,630 --> 00:09:54,030
It doesn't hurt as much when you're around.

174
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,830
Keep your voice down.

175
00:10:06,430 --> 00:10:07,590
They'll hear it.

176
00:10:09,750 --> 00:10:10,480
They can't.

177
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:18,210
I'm sorry.

178
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:20,430
I've already heard your words.

179
00:10:21,050 --> 00:10:21,550
Jie.

180
00:10:21,570 --> 00:10:21,960
Jie.

181
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:22,740
What did you hear?

182
00:10:22,740 --> 00:10:23,480
Nothing, nothing.

183
00:10:23,480 --> 00:10:23,740
Jie.

184
00:10:23,750 --> 00:10:25,030
You didn't hear anything, right?

185
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:25,630
Jie, Jie.

186
00:10:54,220 --> 00:10:56,550
Is this the place you wanted to bring me to?

187
00:10:56,990 --> 00:10:57,400
Yes.

188
00:10:57,550 --> 00:11:00,010
I brought you here to breathe some fresh air.

189
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:02,410
I thought you wanted a romantic date.

190
00:11:04,530 --> 00:11:06,320
Don't do

191
00:11:06,400 --> 00:11:07,660
what you did last time.

192
00:11:09,900 --> 00:11:10,630
What did I do?

193
00:11:11,740 --> 00:11:12,580
You know it.

194
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,640
Stealing a kiss from you?

195
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:17,390
Shut up.

196
00:11:19,450 --> 00:11:21,050
Didn't you kiss me that time?

197
00:11:21,270 --> 00:11:22,730
You're talking nonsense.

198
00:11:39,880 --> 00:11:41,810
This time, it wasn't a stolen kiss.

199
00:12:22,630 --> 00:12:24,690
Jiang Bohan, you did that on purpose.

200
00:12:33,200 --> 00:12:33,930
Jiang Bohan,

201
00:12:34,360 --> 00:12:35,410
where is the highest place

202
00:12:35,410 --> 00:12:36,440
you've been to?

203
00:12:37,950 --> 00:12:38,590
The

204
00:12:38,800 --> 00:12:39,660
highest place?

205
00:12:40,440 --> 00:12:41,770
Commercial airliners.

206
00:12:41,980 --> 00:12:45,600
The typical cruising altitude is between 8,000 and 10,000 meters.

207
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:47,460
I'm talking about a place on land.

208
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:49,750
It would be

209
00:12:50,120 --> 00:12:51,910
Mauna Kea Volcano in Hawaii.

210
00:12:52,750 --> 00:12:54,220
If we don't count elevation,

211
00:12:54,220 --> 00:12:56,890
it is the tallest mountain in the world.

212
00:12:59,850 --> 00:13:01,660
The highest place I've been to

213
00:13:02,130 --> 00:13:03,370
is probably here.

214
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:23,110
It's okay.

215
00:13:23,970 --> 00:13:27,170
You will have many opportunities to travel in the future.

216
00:13:28,240 --> 00:13:28,790
I

217
00:13:29,320 --> 00:13:31,180
don't want to wait for the future.

218
00:13:31,200 --> 00:13:33,000
I want to go out and see the world.

219
00:13:35,080 --> 00:13:35,810
Jiang Bohan,

220
00:13:38,670 --> 00:13:40,130
let's go abroad together.

221
00:13:41,510 --> 00:13:43,640
Why are you suddenly mentioning this?

222
00:13:44,840 --> 00:13:46,960
My dad borrowed a lot of money

223
00:13:47,750 --> 00:13:49,210
and got into debt to invest

224
00:13:49,260 --> 00:13:50,990
to make me go to Jingcai College

225
00:13:51,380 --> 00:13:52,840
and see the outside world.

226
00:13:53,510 --> 00:13:54,510
So,

227
00:13:55,140 --> 00:13:56,400
I want to study abroad.

228
00:13:56,830 --> 00:13:58,710
It's also a way to fulfil his wish.

229
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:02,440
Why haven't you mentioned this before?

230
00:14:03,140 --> 00:14:04,530
You know

231
00:14:05,630 --> 00:14:06,830
my family situation.

232
00:14:08,910 --> 00:14:09,770
What about now?

233
00:14:11,960 --> 00:14:12,760
A few days ago,

234
00:14:13,290 --> 00:14:15,090
Senior Dong Zihui came to see me.

235
00:14:16,000 --> 00:14:16,790
She said

236
00:14:17,160 --> 00:14:19,030
she wanted me to go abroad with you.

237
00:14:19,030 --> 00:14:19,870
She's willing

238
00:14:20,290 --> 00:14:22,020
to cover my tuition fees first.

239
00:14:23,190 --> 00:14:23,920
Don't worry.

240
00:14:26,030 --> 00:14:26,830
I'll deal with

241
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,530
the money issue.

242
00:14:30,360 --> 00:14:32,090
I want to get the money on my own.

243
00:14:32,240 --> 00:14:34,300
I can apply for school scholarships.

244
00:14:35,180 --> 00:14:37,380
I don't want to owe anyone else anymore.

245
00:14:57,780 --> 00:14:59,020
Didn't you say

246
00:14:59,390 --> 00:15:00,670
you want to go to UCLA?

247
00:15:03,270 --> 00:15:03,750
Yeah.

248
00:15:05,140 --> 00:15:07,270
After my younger brother passed away,

249
00:15:08,380 --> 00:15:09,540
I blamed my mom.

250
00:15:10,270 --> 00:15:12,350
I thought it was all her fault.

251
00:15:15,390 --> 00:15:16,920
I rejected her suggestions

252
00:15:16,960 --> 00:15:18,720
because I wanted to spite her.

253
00:15:22,080 --> 00:15:23,000
But later,

254
00:15:23,000 --> 00:15:24,790
I joined the Jingcai College basketball team

255
00:15:24,790 --> 00:15:26,520
and attended the youth league.

256
00:15:27,080 --> 00:15:29,080
I couldn't abandon my teammates

257
00:15:30,010 --> 00:15:31,370
and let down my team

258
00:15:31,690 --> 00:15:33,290
for the sake of my own dreams.

259
00:15:34,880 --> 00:15:35,550
So,

260
00:15:36,140 --> 00:15:37,540
after this competition,

261
00:15:37,790 --> 00:15:40,050
you can think about going abroad, right?

262
00:15:41,140 --> 00:15:42,000
What about you?

263
00:15:44,510 --> 00:15:45,200
I...

264
00:15:45,220 --> 00:15:46,300
I will definitely do

265
00:15:46,300 --> 00:15:47,300
what I promised.

266
00:16:01,810 --> 00:16:03,000
It's a deal.

267
00:16:10,910 --> 00:16:11,710
That's great.

268
00:16:12,120 --> 00:16:13,190
In a few days,

269
00:16:13,590 --> 00:16:16,030
you'll go play in the basketball tournament,

270
00:16:16,030 --> 00:16:18,160
and I'll participate in the marathon.

271
00:16:18,240 --> 00:16:19,200
We'll both have

272
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:20,480
a bright future.

273
00:16:22,950 --> 00:16:28,540
♪ All of my dreams, leading me here ♪

274
00:16:23,010 --> 00:16:24,120
Then, let's

275
00:16:26,270 --> 00:16:27,400
cheer each other on.

276
00:16:29,270 --> 00:16:34,280
♪ All that I gave up just to stand where I stand ♪

277
00:16:35,440 --> 00:16:41,290
♪ And every step that I took was towards you ♪

278
00:16:56,950 --> 00:16:57,600
Today,

279
00:16:57,600 --> 00:16:58,640
let's say goodbye here.

280
00:16:58,640 --> 00:16:59,190
It's too late.

281
00:16:59,190 --> 00:17:00,450
You should go back now.

282
00:17:01,480 --> 00:17:04,010
I always walk you up to your apartment before.

283
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:05,920
Today is different.

284
00:17:07,030 --> 00:17:07,829
Why?

285
00:17:09,190 --> 00:17:10,950
The weather forecast says

286
00:17:11,200 --> 00:17:12,599
it's going to rain tonight.

287
00:17:12,599 --> 00:17:14,160
You have a game coming up soon.

288
00:17:14,160 --> 00:17:15,109
Don't catch a cold.

289
00:17:15,109 --> 00:17:16,640
Or I'll be worried.

290
00:17:17,829 --> 00:17:18,359
Alright.

291
00:17:19,010 --> 00:17:20,000
Go back by yourself, then.

292
00:17:20,000 --> 00:17:21,000
I'm heading home.

293
